hyperscan (5.4.2-1+kernel-module) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Enable unit tests in the CI builds
  * Add ExpressionLib to the package as it is required for loading
    databases into the kernel
  * Disable AVX512 support, since the kernel runtime is set to not use it.
    Otherwise the databases are compiled with the AVX512 and can't be
    loaded into the kernel.
  * Set Gcore as maintainers of this fork

 -- Ivan Koveshnikov <ivan.koveshnikov@gcore.com>  Mon, 15 Apr 2024 22:30:11 +0100

